transcript:
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Haan, sir, main ye keh raha tha aapki mail to aa gayi mere paas ye 53000 rupay wali.
Customer: Haan ji.
Executive: Isme koi image attach hoke nahi aayi hai lekin.
Customer: Do mail bheji hai maine.
Executive: Do mail bheji hai? Mail sir ek hi aayi hai mere paas lekin.
Customer: Ek hi aayi hai. Koi nahi main abhi thodi der tak bhijwata hu dusri bhi.
Executive: Theek hai sir, theek hai. 
Customer: Theek hai ya whatsapp kar du?
Executive: Haan whatsapp kar diyo usse better kya hai.
Customer: Ek baar mere ko isi number pe hi likhna main drive kar raha tha.
Executive: Number bolna sir mujhe abhi aapka number show nahi hoga bolna ek baar. 
Customer: 8805
Executive: 805
Customer: 989
Executive: 989
Customer: 1111
Executive: 1111
Customer: Theek hai, main isme aapko sari detail whatsapp kar deta hu.
Executive: Theek hai sir, okay.
Customer: Theek hai.
